He was a success with women in those years.
All the girls were fat when he was around", says Hairston, now 40, who lives in the Brandon suburb of Jackson.
Lamb and Prentiss must have been dating for a while at the time.
Lamb said in the 911 call, "I killed my wife", but there's no marriage registration.
The couple had a dog named Lightning, who lived with them in Goethe in a brick house with a backside overlooking the canal.
