So the Greek ministers were not prepared and they were not well informed, and so they failed to negotiate and they failed to make a deal.
Euronews: If you win the election, you will soon be sitting at the same table with Mr. Juncker, Mr. Hollande, Mrs. Merkel and other European leaders.
