David Cameron's reckless policy of resuming the negotiations on Britain's stay in the EU is getting more and more difficult every day, even without looking at the election of the brilliant Jeremy - "Is that yes or no?" - Corbyn as Labour leader or TUC's outrage over Europe on Tuesday.
Foreigners have their Corbin and Nigella Farage too.
